  <brief_title>Examining The Effect of Blood Flow Restricted Aerobic Training on Mitochondrial Adaptations in Young Healthy Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>Examining The Effect of Blood Flow Restricted Aerobic Training on Citrate Synthase Activity in Young Healthy Adults</official_title>
