  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This parallel-arm trial study investigates the effects of restricting arterial blood flow&#xD;
      during cycling exercise on citrate synthase. Participants will be randomized to either a&#xD;
      blood flow restricted or non-blood flow restricted exercise training group. Both groups will&#xD;
      complete seven, 30-minute exercise sessions over a 14-day period.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
